folder.description: Carries all purchase journey related dynamic pages.
Holds any editorial pages, which do not relate to dynamic shop areas such as my account or checkout or are assigned to the product discovery journey

The products are assigned to specific classification-like categories, that will determine the PD Page to show. For product sets, YSH chose that way to create a page that is optimized for a set - i.e. often found as a look in fashion shops
Pages related to themes and general page elements visible accross multiple pages
